author: Msnbc
title: Can Trump 'override' states' pandemic decisions? Will he?
description: When states balk at stay-at-home orders, Trump emphasizes "federalism." When they're prepared to maintain the orders, his emphasis is ... different.
content: During the White House's press briefing on April 4, a reporter noted that a number of governors, each of whom are Republicans, "have refused to issue these statewide stay-at-home orders." The journalist asked Donald Trump why he simply doesn't urge these alli… [+2542 chars]
